{
  "stem": "26022.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they all played with me, talked to me, sang to me, took me for walks, made pretty birthday parties.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I do remember my 4th birthday very vividly because one aunt-- and that was my father's sister, who passed away still during the war.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this is a very far away memory of her, lady with a high collar.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got a beautiful winter coat that I thought was lined in gold like all these fairy tales.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Actually, that was some kind of a yellow lining fabric.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I do remember that birthday when I got the coat lined in gold.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So your childhood was-- you were surrounded by adults.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did you have opportunities to play with young children?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, there-- either there were none or they might carry germs or stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in my early childhood, I was not given an opportunity to play with children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I went to school when I was six.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was right after the war when the big Austro-Hungarian empire shrank to the little Republic of Austria that I know as the country where I grew up.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And many refugees-- they all came to Vienna, which had been their capital.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there wasn't enough housing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I really caught every germ that went around so that after a few months where I was more sick than well-- and a very fast-growing, very thin child.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And food wasn't always available.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And these were bad times.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my parents took me out of school and had me tutored, which means a lady came one hour a day.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then at the end of the school year, I had to pass an exam in the regular public school to be advanced to the next level.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
